{"descriptions":[{"id":1333,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eAdjectives can be transformed into adverbs by the addition of the suffix \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱས་\u003c/span\u003e, which is derived from the verb \u0026ldquo;to do\u0026rdquo;:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྐྱིད་པོ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Pleasant\u0026rdquo; \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསྐྱིད་པོ་བྱས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Pleasantly\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྷོད་ལྷོད་བྱས་བཞུགས་དོ།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Let\u0026rsquo;s sit here quietly.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:39 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}